{{! Full club logo: bull-icon chip + "skotovody." wordmark + "КЛУБ" badge.
    Renders in before-header-panel, right after the (CSS-hidden) #site-logo image.

    The mockup (docs/Club_Skotovody/club/club-atoms.jsx → ClubLogo) defines the
    brand mark as a text wordmark, not a raster image — so we port that directly
    instead of relying on an uploaded logo (the uploaded PNG is light-on-white
    and effectively invisible).

    Connector filename (sktvd-club-1-logo-badge) deliberately differs from the
    styled root class (.sktvd-club-logo) so the outlet wrapper stays unstyled. }}
